data.description: SELLER TO CREDIT BUYER FULL ROOF REPLACEMENT-DETAILS IN AGENT NOTES. One of the largest ranch homes in the neighborhood! So much to love about this updated 3 bedroom, 2 full bath 1-level home! Beautiful curb appeal with timeless exterior color scheme with covered entry and storm door. Spacious open living/kitchen/dining space with new LVP flooring, kitchen features stainless steel appliances and separate pantry. Large master with walk-in closet with wood shelving and ensuite. Both full baths have been updated with new LVP flooring, vanity and toilet. Separate laundry room. New 1" faux wood cordless blinds. Enjoy the outdoor living space with back yard patio, deck, privacy fence & storage shed. 2-car garage with epoxy floor and keypad entry. Everything you need on 1 level!
